  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/48c5865162cb13039a06d9a1a2291923.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/48c5865162cb13039a06d9a1a2291923.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity in Park Studio, the next generation of Theme Park simulation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience true creative freedom as you build, decorate and customize the parks of your dreams, with an unprecedented level of detail and unmatched realism!<br><br>Get creative now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/96c1e0c730a7ad74df80d8475f9803d9.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/96c1e0c730a7ad74df80d8475f9803d9.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Construct the ultimate ride:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create thrilling roller coasters with ease using the coaster builder or import your existing creations from other programs using the CSV importer, the choice is yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Impress the crowd:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Special Track Elements such as bounce tracks, drop tracks and more to enhance your ride experience and amaze your visitors*!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*: Visitors are currently not available</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/fad908d8d71d58624facb5e489d19d97.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/fad908d8d71d58624facb5e489d19d97.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build amazing structures:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct incredible structures to house your rides and facilities* using the large library of building pieces available in the game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate your park:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your park with the extensive library of scenery pieces, create stunning theming for your rides or add impressive details to your structures with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*: Facilities are currently not available</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/af5d5e81a7ebc657154d3907d9f176fe.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/af5d5e81a7ebc657154d3907d9f176fe.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Always more to come:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Park Studio is currently in Alpha, features are getting added update after update and more content will be available as development progresses. Join the community to learn more and discuss everything about the game! <br><br>And stay tuned for future updates!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/48c5865162cb13039a06d9a1a2291923.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/48c5865162cb13039a06d9a1a2291923.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity in Park Studio, the next generation of Theme Park simulation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience true creative freedom as you build, decorate and customize the parks of your dreams, with an unprecedented level of detail and unmatched realism!<br><br>Get creative now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/96c1e0c730a7ad74df80d8475f9803d9.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/96c1e0c730a7ad74df80d8475f9803d9.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Construct the ultimate ride:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create thrilling roller coasters with ease using the coaster builder or import your existing creations from other programs using the CSV importer, the choice is yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Impress the crowd:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Special Track Elements such as bounce tracks, drop tracks and more to enhance your ride experience and amaze your visitors*!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*: Visitors are currently not available</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/fad908d8d71d58624facb5e489d19d97.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/fad908d8d71d58624facb5e489d19d97.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build amazing structures:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construct incredible structures to house your rides and facilities* using the large library of building pieces available in the game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Decorate your park:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your park with the extensive library of scenery pieces, create stunning theming for your rides or add impressive details to your structures with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*: Facilities are currently not available</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras/af5d5e81a7ebc657154d3907d9f176fe.avif?t=1733497918\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832220/extras_big/af5d5e81a7ebc657154d3907d9f176fe.avif?t=1733497918 width=800 height=106 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Always more to come:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Park Studio is currently in Alpha, features are getting added update after update and more content will be available as development progresses. Join the community to learn more and discuss everything about the game! <br><br>And stay tuned for future updates!</p>",
